*Novcem* je kupio novi auto. (He bought a new car with money.)
On je *novcem* popravio svoj stan. (He fixed his apartment with money.)
Ona je *novcem* platila kiriju. (She paid the rent with money.)
*Novcem* je plaćao i račune. (He was paying bills with money.)
Oni su *novcem* pomogli prijatelju. (They helped a friend with money.)